Normalisation

\(x_{i,j}=\frac{WindowCoverage_{i,j}\times10^{9}}{WindowLength_{i}\times{totalReadsSample_{j}}}\)

\(xnorm_{i,j}=\frac{x_{i,j}}{mean(X_{i})}\)
